This directory contains ligand and receptor coordinates extracted
from the 1ABE entry in the Brookhaven Protein DataBase.

                             --- * ---

1ABE.pdb            Original pdb entry of complex
lig_charged.mol2    ligand with AM1BCC charges calculated
rec_noH.mol2        receptor without hydrogens
rec_charged.mol2    receptor with hydrogens added and AMBER parm94 charges

